Module kingdoms.kingdoms
Package kingdoms.kingdoms

Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • kingdoms.kingdoms.Person
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ruler
    public abstract class Person
extends java.lang.Object

    Class implementing a teoretical person. Because aa ordinary person has no use in this game, a person cannot be created. It serves only as template for a ruler

    Person has only an age

    Author:
    Jakub Niewiarowski
